---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="API" description="Overview of the HelixGitpx API surface.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold">API</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">Two ways to talk to HelixGitpx: Connect-RPC or REST. Same contracts, different wires.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold">Connect-RPC (preferred)</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">Schema-first via Protobuf. Streaming supported. TypeScript, Go, Swift, Kotlin clients generated by <code>buf</code>.</p>
    <pre class="mt-3 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded text-sm overflow-auto"><code>import {'{'} createClient {'}'} from "@connectrpc/connect";
import {'{'} createConnectTransport {'}'} from "@connectrpc/connect-web";
import {'{'} OrgService {'}'} from "@helixgitpx/proto";

const orgs = createClient(OrgService, createConnectTransport({'{'}
  baseUrl: "https://api.helixgitpx.io",
  credentials: "include",
{'}'}));

await orgs.list({'{'}{'}'});</code></pre>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold">REST (OpenAPI)</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">Auto-generated from the same protos via <code>buf.build/grpc-ecosystem/openapiv2</code>.</p>
    <pre class="mt-3 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded text-sm overflow-auto"><code>GET  /api/v1/orgs                Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;
POST /api/v1/orgs                Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;
POST /api/v1/repos/:id/bindings  Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;
</code></pre>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold">Rate limits</h2>
    <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Free: 60 req / min / token.</li>
      <li>Team: 600 req / min / token.</li>
      <li>Scale: 6,000 req / min / token.</li>
      <li>Enterprise: negotiated.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-10 text-slate-600">
      Deep reference on <a href="https://docs.helixgitpx.io" class="text-primary hover:underline">docs.helixgitpx.io</a>.
      Schemas in <code>impl/helixgitpx/proto/</code>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
